 "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Oh no, I need a 3D printer now", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-18T14:43:26+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Blizzard Entertainment\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/24533771/Druid_Legendaries.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p><strong>Druids</strong> are one of the most interesting classes in <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/diablo-4-guides/23933512/guide-tips-locations\"><em>Diablo 4</em></a>. They\u2019re not only able to control animals \u2014 they can turn <em>into</em> animals (and also cast powerful spells). The result is a class that\u2019s packed with complex ability combinations that can deal massive damage. As such, designing an ideal Druid build is a puzzle in its own right. That\u2019s where we come in, with our suggestions of the best Druid builds for <em>Diablo 4</em> season 6.</p>\n\n<p>Druids can cast storm spells, control the earth, summon companions, or sha", "id": 1350025, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/diablo-4-guides/23656236/druid-best-build-skills", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Best Druid builds in Diablo 4 season 6", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-18T14:43:21+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t